      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit delivers a visceral 414 hp with a peak 8,400 RPM redline, paired to a lightning-fast 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring surgical precision through the apex. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive throttle actuator service and a cooling system refresh. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical synchronization and compression remain excellent. This is a robust, mechanically sound example of the last atmospheric M3, ready for the B-roads.",
